Class SpokeExpansion

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComplexExpansionMethod<Interaction,BinaryInteraction>

    public class SpokeExpansion
extends AbstractSpokeExpansion<Interaction,BinaryInteraction>
    The spoke expansion Complex n-ary data has been expanded to binary using the spoke model. This assumes that all molecules in the complex interact with a single designated molecule, usually the bait.
    Since:
    05/06/13
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Marine Dumousseau (marine@ebi.ac.uk)
